{"tid":801953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與妻爭執 39歲兩子之父觀塘跳海死亡","createTime":"2018-09-01T05:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T05:47:30.000Z","uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"620a4ce64485d50b48c128794f5abaa1c24cc33d","tid":801953,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"與妻爭執 39歲兩子之父觀塘跳海死亡 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/806692-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%88%87%E5%A6%BB%E7%88%AD%E5%9F%B7+39%E6%AD%B2%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%8B%E7%88%B6%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E8%B7%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F806692-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%259F%25B7%2B39%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%20&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8d779392\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F806692-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%259F%25B7%2B39%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%20&h=8fc8dfc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/806692-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%88%87%E5%A6%BB%E7%88%AD%E5%9F%B7+39%E6%AD%B2%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%8B%E7%88%B6%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E8%B7%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1 </a><br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，事主由警方和消防救起。 <br />\n<br />\n一名育有兩子的39歲男子，懷疑與妻子發生爭執後，早上留下遺書，在觀塘海濱道一碼頭跳海死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n警方早上6時25接獲途人報案，指懷疑事主在碼頭墮海。警員接報到場，事主由警方和消防救起，昏迷送聯合醫院治理後被證實死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n警方於現場檢獲遺書。經初步調查，相信事件沒有可疑。死因有待驗屍後確定。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，事主跳海前曾在碼頭一帶徘徊，之後放下物品便在碼頭跳下海中，途人一度拋下水泡協助救援。"},{"pid":